WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.266 --> 00:00:05.200
Mom mom

2
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.400
My good sister is so worried about you.

3
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:10.300
My little chicken mother finally found you

4
00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:12.500
Chicken thank you

5
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.633
Why is a chicken that refuses to speak?

6
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:20.100
Think of his mother

7
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.766
What are you doing in the middle of the night in a panic?

8
00:00:27.533 --> 00:00:29.766
Mom, I was killed and admitted to the hospital

9
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:30.900
What did you hurt?

10
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.166
Isn't that beast dead?

11
00:00:33.166 --> 00:00:35.400
Dad, he's not just back

12
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:38.400
He also tried his best to ruin my marriage to Yard

13
00:00:38.666 --> 00:00:40.233
He's just jealous of me

14
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.900
He is coming to take revenge on the entire Xia family this time

15
00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:47.000
This beast has shamed our Xia family

16
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.200
He still has the face to come back

17
00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:52.700
Lao Xia, don't be angry.

18
00:00:53.066 --> 00:00:54.600
The smoke died early

19
00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.800
It's my stepmother who didn't say it well

20
00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:58.166
I think so.

21
00:00:58.200 --> 00:00:59.366
This woman

22
00:00:59.366 --> 00:01:02.233
As long as you are married, you must be sensible

23
00:01:02.666 --> 00:01:04.966
Then he won't be married

24
00:01:06.133 --> 00:01:08.766
Well, that makes sense.

25
00:01:09.100 --> 00:01:11.300
Let him marry Mr. Li

